msg.msgText:
A "Plugin" can be deleted using the "delete" option of the "imaserver" command.
SYNTAX: imaserver delete Plugin help imaserver delete Plugin "Name=value"
EXAMPLE: imaserver delete Plugin "Name=json_msg"
NOTE: To get a list of protocol plug-ins, use "imaserver list Plugin" command.
